# UI Components & Design System

TaskHub follows a consistent design system with reusable components.

## Core UI Components

- **CustomTextFormField** - Standard text input with customizable prefix/suffix icons
- **PrimaryButton** - Main action button with standardized styling
- **CustomDropdown** - Styled dropdown menu component

## Color Palette

- **primaryColor** - Purple (`Color(0xff673AB7)`) - Main brand color
- **black** - Black (`Color(0xff000000)`) - Used for text and key elements
- **white** - White (`Color(0xffffffff)`) - Background and contrast elements
- **textformfill** - Light gray (`Color(0xffaeaeae).withOpacity(0.1)`) - Form field backgrounds
- **greyColor1/2/3** - Various gray shades for different UI elements

## Typography

- Uses the **Geist** font family throughout the app
- Standard text sizes:
  - Headers: 28px
  - Subheaders: 18px
  - Body text: 16px
  - Small text: 14px

## Form Pattern

All forms follow a consistent pattern:
1. Label text with standard styling
2. SizedBox with height 8
3. CustomTextFormField with appropriate prefixIcon
4. SizedBox with height 16 between fields

When implementing UI, always use these existing components and patterns for consistency.

